{"id":126418,"type":6,"name":"听见你的声音","summary":"剧中还是8岁的男主角朴修夏和当时是高中生的张彗星目睹了修夏的父亲被闵俊国杀害的场景，张彗星受到了闵俊国的威胁，但是仍然在法庭上指证了闵俊国的罪行，闵俊国也因此被判刑十年。但是闵俊国扬言出狱后会报复彗星和修夏，修夏许诺一定要守护彗星，此后两人就再也没有见过面，但是修夏一直追寻彗星的下落。十年之后，张彗星成为国选律师，闵俊国刑满出狱，发誓要找修夏和彗星报仇。而与此同时修夏也找到彗星，并利用自己的读心术，帮助彗星破解了一个又一个案件，同时闵俊国的一系列阴谋也使得修夏和彗星的命运紧紧连在一起，两人在相处中渐渐产生了爱情并最终走到一起。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>听见你的声音</li><li><span>别名: </span>I Hear Your Voice</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>너의 목소리가 들려</li><li><span>集数: </span>18</li><li><span>开始: </span>2013年6月5日</li><li><span>类型: </span>爱情</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>韩国</li><li><span>语言: </span>韩语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>70min</li><li><span>电视台: </span>SBS</li><li><span>首播国家: </span>韩国</li>","eps":[{"id":486248,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486248","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486249,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486249","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486250,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486250","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486251,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486251","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486252,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486252","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486253,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486253","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486254,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486254","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486255,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486255","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":486256,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/486256","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","n